caption.text:
*I had to repost because I edit the pict so that the name becomes the title*
.
.
Okay, so this is Owen. He is the main character on my next 3D Animation Production class where we have to make 1 minute animation short individually. I did lots of experiment on his looks - trying new style etc. My teacher likes the third design, so I made the action pose, but I didn't really "click" with the character so I explore a bit more and here he is, coloured and rendered digitally (still 2D tho). .
.
.
His name is Owen because he will be opening lots and lots of boxes in the animation. Stay tuned! I too, looking forward to model him. Hope it turns out well :D.
.
.
